title: Team News: Zoet replaces Krul for Netherlands
text:
Team News: Zoet replaces Krul for Netherlands Â© Getty Images Jeroen Zoet comes into the Netherlands starting lineup to replace the injured Tim Krul in his side's Euro 2016 qualifying clash against the Czech Republic. Filed: Tuesday, October 13, 2015 at 18:58 UK Last Updated: Tuesday, October 13, 2015 at 18:58 UK 
Jeroen Zoet comes into the Netherlands starting lineup to replace the injured Tim Krul in his side's Euro 2016 qualifying clash against the Czech Republic . 
Netherlands: Zoet; Tete, Bruma, van Dijk, Riedewald; Wijnaldum, Blind, Sneijder, El Ghazi; Huntelaar, DepaySubs: Vermeer, van der Wiel, Anita, Rekik, Kongolo, Bazoer, Lens, Dost, van Persie, Afellay, Elia, Stekelenburg 
Czech Republic: Cech; Kaderabek, Suchy, Kadlec, Gebre Selassie; Skalak, Darida, Pavelka, Plasil; Sural, NecidSubs: Vaclik, Prochazka, Kalas, Frydek, Skoda, Petrzela, Kopic, Krejci, Novak, Koubek
